videoSnippet.title: Tal's Record in Danger! | Ding Liren vs Svidler  | ECCC (2018)
videoSnippet.description:
Follow me on Instagram for extra content: https://www.instagram.com/agadmator/

Check out the score between any player here http://www.chessgames.com

Liren Ding vs Peter Svidler
EUROPEAN CLUB CUP 2018, Greece, Porto Carras Grand Resort 
15 Oct 2018.
King's Indian Defense: Alekhine Anti-Grunfeld (D70)

1. d4 Nf6 2. c4 g6 3. f3 Nc6 4. d5 Ne5 5. e4 d6 6. Nc3 c6 7. f4 Ned7 8. Nh3 Nc5 9. Nf2 Bg7 10. Be2 O-O 11. Be3 cxd5 12. cxd5 Qa5 13. O-O Bd7 14. e5 Ne8 15. Qd4 Na4 16. Nxa4 Qxa4 17. Rac1 Qa5 18. Ne4 Bb5 19. Bxb5 Qxb5 20. b3 dxe5 21. fxe5 Nd6 22. Bf4 Rac8 23. Nc3 Qa5 24. Qd3 Nf5 25. g4 Qb6+ 26. Kh1 Qd4 27. Qe4 Qxe4+ 28. Nxe4 Nd4 29. Rcd1 Ne2 30. Bg5 f6 31. exf6 exf6 32. Nxf6+ Bxf6 33. Bxf6 Nc3 34. Rd4 Rcd8 35. Bxd8 Rxf1+ 36. Kg2 Rf7 37. d6 Rd7 38. Bg5 Nxa2 39. Bd2 b5 40. b4 Kf7 41. Rd3

34th European Club Cup and the 23rd European Women Club Cup will be simultaneously held from 11th-19th October 2018 in Porto Carras, famous Greek seaside resort in Halkidiki.

Official page http://www.europechess.org/european-club-cup-2018-regulations/
